item.title: PLEASE need help i can get on my server but other ppl not
item.dc:creator: @zyle1992 Zymus
item.description:
@zyle1992 wrote:

There’s some key things you need to do.

If you haven’t already:

[] Register, Download and install No-IP here
[] Check if your server port is open here
[] Tell your players to enter your no-ip address into their client
[] Ensure that your server is running on the correc port

If all those things check out, ensure that you don’t have any other programs on your computer listening to the server port.
